{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Analyzes a selected MIDI item and generates a dedicated "Chords" track. Uses pitch-class sets (modulo 12) for multi-octave robustness, combined with a smart dictionary that detects inversions, dyads, and calculates accurate slash chords.\par}
